Chapter 3 - Score Ranks

Table of Rankings
score	rank
0	"Beginner"
25	"Amateur Adventurer"
50	"Novice Adventurer"
100	"Junior Adventurer"
200	"Adventurer"
300	"Master"
330	"Wizard"
